OL,3,CWoman trying for baby prescribed wrong
OL,4,Cdrugs that can cause miscarriage
OL,6,FShe was wrongly prescribed powerful
OL,7,Fdrugs that can cause birth defects and
OL,8,Fmiscarriages, despite trying for a
OL,9,Fbaby.
OL,11,FCharlotte explains: "It's only because
OL,12,Fmy friend's sister-in-law is a
OL,13,Frheumatologist in the UK, my friend
OL,14,Fspoke to her and that's how I found
OL,15,Fout. It wasn't because the doctors
OL,16,Frealised and when they did, there was
OL,17,Fno apology or follow-up.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
