OL,3,CWoman trying for baby prescribed wrong
OL,4,Cdrugs that can cause miscarriage
OL,6,F"I couldn't believe it, I'm very vocal
OL,7,Fabout wanting children, it's the first
OL,8,Fthing I discuss whenever I see a
OL,9,Fprofessional. To have a drug that
OL,10,Fcould lead to birth defects is
OL,11,Fabsolutely disgusting, no follow-up is
OL,12,Feven worse.
OL,14,F"Secondly, I was on steroids for over
OL,15,Ftwo years with no suggestion of me
OL,16,Fcoming off, I took myself off those
OL,17,Fbecause I felt it wasn't having an
OL,18,Fimpact and we know the implication of
OL,19,Fsteroids on people and their health.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
