OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F382A1721744256
OL,3,CWoman trying for baby prescribed wrong
OL,4,Cdrugs that can cause miscarriage
OL,6,F"Then I was put onto another really
OL,7,Fpowerful drug and when I saw another
OL,8,Fdoctor we had a discussion about it
OL,9,Fnot being the best for me. I'd been on
OL,10,Fthat for over a year."
OL,12,FCharlotte now has twins and is still a
OL,13,Fpatient in Jersey's Rheumatology
OL,14,FService but feels like her life is in
OL,15,Flimbo.
