OL,3,CWoman trying for baby prescribed wrong
OL,4,Cdrugs that can cause miscarriage
OL,6,FShe adds: "I don't know what the long-
OL,7,Fterm implications of being on those
OL,8,Fdrugs are, I have got other issues
OL,9,Fgoing on, is that a result of being on
OL,10,Fthis medication? I don't know. I don't
OL,11,Fknow what the long-term impact is of
OL,12,Fbeing on a very powerful medication
OL,13,Fthat I shouldn't have been on.
OL,15,F"I feel grateful that I'm alive but
OL,16,Fequally I feel that there's been an
OL,17,Finjustice because I still don't know
OL,18,Fwhat's wrong with me and I haven't got
OL,19,Fthe correct treatment plan in place so
OL,20,FI'm still in pain, still suffering and
OL,21,Fwe're no further forward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
