OL,3,CWoman trying for baby prescribed wrong
OL,4,Cdrugs that can cause miscarriage
OL,6,F"The compensation claims are secondary
OL,7,Fto most people who are in constant
OL,8,Fpain. When it's affecting your daily
OL,9,Flife, what you actually want is just
OL,10,Fto feel better."
OL,12,FThe experience has also undermined
OL,13,FCharlotte's belief in doctors.
OL,15,FShe says: "You look to medical
OL,16,Fprofessionals as the experts and this
OL,17,Fjust shows that unfortunately, we have
OL,18,Fto question every step of the way and
OL,19,Fhave the confidence to be able to
OL,20,Fchallenge them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
