OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F382A1721744256
OL,3,CWoman trying for baby prescribed wrong
OL,4,Cdrugs that can cause miscarriage
OL,6,F"I feel angry that we're years down
OL,7,Fthe line and I'm still no further
OL,8,Fforward as to what can be done to make
OL,9,Fme feel better and I'm sure many
OL,10,Fothers feel the same."
OL,12,FMedical Director Patrick Armstrong has
OL,13,Fdescribed the rheumatology failings as
OL,14,Fa "scandal" and promised compensation.
OL,16,FHe has reassured patients that the
OL,17,Fdepartment has improved hugely and 16
OL,18,Fof the 26 recommendations made by the
OL,19,FRoyal College of Physicians have
OL,20,Falready been brought in.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
