OL,6,FHowever, no staff members have been
OL,7,Flet go with Mr Armstrong telling ITV
OL,8,FNews, "I don't think sacking people
OL,9,Fcreates real change, I think that
OL,10,Fmakes people fearful and we've done an
OL,11,Fawful lot of work trying to create a
OL,12,Fculture where people feel empowered
OL,13,Fand safe to speak up so sacking people
OL,14,Fisn't always the answer."
